Package: rk3588-rt-middleware
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: RK3588 Industrial Toolkit Team <1513741889@qq.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-numpy, util-linux (>= 2.34)
Recommends: linux-image-rt-arm64 | linux-image-6.1.75-rt
Description: RK3588 Industrial Protocol Real-Time Middleware
 CPU core isolation, IRQ affinity configuration,
 real-time latency monitoring (jitter analysis),
 and industrial protocol stack integration
 (EtherCAT, Profinet, OPC UA, Modbus).
 .
 Features:
  - CPU isolation with AMP support (A55 + A76)
  - IRQ affinity for deterministic latency
  - Cyclictest-style jitter monitor (P99 < 50us target)
  - IgH EtherCAT Master auto-installer
  - PREEMPT_RT kernel build automation
 .
 Target: RK3588-based industrial controllers
 Requires: PREEMPT_RT kernel for <50us latency
Homepage: https://github.com/yicechuhai/rk3588-industrial-rt-middleware
